HEADWORD: Everyday
<hw>Ev"er*y*day`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Used or fit for
every day; common; usual; <as>as, an <ex>everyday</ex> suit of
clothes</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The mechanical drudgery of his <qex>everyday</qex> employment.</q>
<rj><qau>Sir. J. Herchel.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Everyone</ent>⟦br⟧
